86 template <class Attribute>
87 void TAttributeStaticInfo<Attribute>::AddRelatedMetaId(int metaGroupId, const QByteArray& id, int flags)
88 {
89  IdsToFlagsMap& groupMap = m_relatedInterfacesMap[metaGroupId];
90 
91  IdsToFlagsMap::iterator foundIter = groupMap.find(id);
92  if (foundIter != groupMap.end()){
93  Q_ASSERT((flags & (AF_REFERENCE | AF_FACTORY)) == (foundIter.value() & (AF_REFERENCE | AF_FACTORY))); // factory can be combined with factory only and reference with reference
94 
95  foundIter.value() |= flags & AF_OBLIGATORY; // is obligatory if once obligatory registred is
96  foundIter.value() &= flags | ~AF_NULLABLE; // is nullable if always nullable registred is
97  }
98  else{
99  groupMap[id] = flags;
100  }
101 
102  if (metaGroupId == IComponentStaticInfo::MGI_INTERFACES){
103  m_attributeFlags |= flags & AF_OBLIGATORY; // attribute is obligatory if one of declared interfaces obligatory is
104  m_attributeFlags &= flags | ~AF_NULLABLE; // attribute is nullable if all of declared interfaces nullable are
105  }
106 }

132 template <class Attribute>
133 IElementStaticInfo::Ids TAttributeStaticInfo<Attribute>::GetRelatedMetaIds(int metaGroupId, int flags, int flagsMask) const
134 {
135  IElementStaticInfo::Ids retVal;
136 
137  RelatedIdsMap::ConstIterator foundGroupIter = m_relatedInterfacesMap.constFind(metaGroupId);
138  if (foundGroupIter != m_relatedInterfacesMap.constEnd()){
139  const IdsToFlagsMap& groupMap = foundGroupIter.value();
140 
141  for ( IdsToFlagsMap::const_iterator iter = groupMap.begin();
142  iter != groupMap.end();
143  ++iter){
144  const QByteArray& id = iter.key();
145  int idFlags = iter.value();
146 
147  if (((idFlags & flagsMask) == flags)){
148  retVal.insert(id);
149  }
150  }
151  }
152 
153  return retVal;
154 }
